    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and factory limited-slip differential, providing an analog and engaging driving experience. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and valve clearance adjustment. The chassis remains rigid with a verified subframe, and the suspension geometry is tight, ensuring the precise turn-in these cars are known for. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the powertrain and drivetrain integrity make this a premier candidate for the discerning enthusiast.",
