    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances executive comfort with dependable performance. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only the minor stone chips and faint surface marks consistent with careful highway driving. There are no major dents or unsightly scratches to detract from its silhouette. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seating is soft and free of punctures or heavy stains, though light character creasing is visible on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, from the responsive infotainment screen to the heated seats and sunroof, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive over bumps. With a fresh set of brake pads and tires that still hold plenty of tread, this car is mechanically sound and ready for immediate use. This is an honest, reliable vehicle for a buyer who values both aesthetics and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34800.0,
